        <h4>Agroecological Forestry</h4>
        <p>The better a place is cared for, the more fruit it gives</p>
        <p>Around the world, communities earn greater incomes and sustain lands for more generations, through agroecological forestry as compared to industrial farming and deforestation.</p>
        <p>Why sell the land, rivers, and forests, when they give us more gifts from our care?</p>
